.Fn X509_REVOKED_set_serialNumber
sets the serial number of
.Fa r
to
.Fa serial .
The supplied
.Fa serial
pointer is not used internally so it should be freed up after use.
.Pp
.Fn X509_REVOKED_set_revocationDate
sets the revocation date of
.Fa r
to
.Fa tm .
